1
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,320
&Manager Hanwen.

2
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,680
Okay, I know.

3
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:35,720
I've contacted the creditors in the group.

4
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:38,320
Someone should go to the school to corner him soon.

5
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:40,120
Spread the news about him

6
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:41,280
giving out loans on campus too.

7
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,920
Spread the news about the loans?

8
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,160
Is it necessary?

9
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:46,640
Mr. Wang is already investigating us in the student council.

10
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:49,240
These student loans will be discovered sooner or later.

11
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:51,500
Now is the best chance to clear our names.

12
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:52,880
I understand.

13
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,160
My dad is in the hospital because of the debt from this project!

14
00:00:57,160 --> 00:01:00,620
And he has the nerve to go back to school like nothing happened!

15
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,200
Excuse me.

16
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,330
Do you know this person?

17
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,880
No, I don't.

18
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,610
Do you know this person?

19
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,840
The damage is quite serious.

20
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,480
I don't know to what extent it can be fixed.

21
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,800
I don't know to what extent it can be fixed.

22
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,920
Tell you what, I'll have someone take it apart and try.

23
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,480
Then when can I get it?

24
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,410
This afternoon.

25
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,530
This afternoon?

26
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:28,000
Should we go see a movie first?

27
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,680
Don't you have classes this afternoon?

28
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,740
I can ask for leave.

29
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:33,660
Plus, don't we have to wait for the phone to be fixed?

30
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,920
It's too much trouble to go back.

31
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:36,840
No.

32
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,440
I'll pick up the phone.

33
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,900
You go back to class first.

34
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,600
This is my number.

35
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,800
Call me when it's fixed.

36
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:46,400
I'll pick it up for her.

37
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:46,920
Okay.

38
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,280
Let's go.

39
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:58,220
It's rare that I've arranged the itinerary.

40
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,320
Zixi.

41
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,200
It's your birthday today.

42
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,400
Do you have any plans?

43
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,080
No.

44
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,600
Then.

45
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,080
Wait for me downstairs at the dorm tonight.

46
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,480
I have some gifts for you.

47
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:19,160
Oh.

48
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,400
What are you guys yelling about?

49
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,480
An Yufan.

50
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,560
Fine if we don't watch a movie,

51
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,800
but you should at least bring my phone back.

52
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,560
Seriously.

53
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,960
You told me to wait for you in the dorm.

54
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,680
I mean,

55
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:45,079
I've been waiting for you all day.

56
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,920
Now look.

57
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,200
I can't leave,

58
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,320
and I can't stay.

59
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,960
The cake and gifts are ready.

60
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,440
What else is missing?

61
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:11,140
I close my eyes and listen to your heartbeat and breathing.

62
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:13,840
And right now, it's just us on Earth.

63
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,620
The shape of your smiling lips always captivates my heart.

64
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:22,480
What does this mean?

65
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,040
Wow, what is going on?

66
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:28,240
Uncle He, aren't you in the hospital?

67
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:30,370
I came specifically to pick you up.

68
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,160
Someone is spreading rumors about you

69
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,920
and organizing creditors to block you at the school gate.

70
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,480
Block me at the school gate?

71
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,640
Why?

72
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,079
Someone wants to stir up news about you

73
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,810
to use you against your father.

74
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,760
I guess you won't be able to return to school for a while.

75
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,440
Pack your luggage and come back with me first.

76
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,040
Boss.

77
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,160
You usually practice with drafts.

78
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,480
Why not this time?

79
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,080
I had guidance from an expert.

80
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,660
Someone actually guided you?

81
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,760
I wasn't bold enough before,

82
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,880
so I had to keep practicing the draft.

83
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,760
Now,

84
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,560
I am ready.

85
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,089
You're not bold enough?

86
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,480
I mean, is this person reliable?

87
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,680
To chase girls.

88
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:26,810
You just need to be bold, attentive, and thick-skinned.

89
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,240
I'm just not bold enough.

90
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,680
Besides being bold,

91
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,280
you also need to be generous.

92
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:34,040
Especially when giving gifts, you must cater to their preferences.

93
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,480
That's what I thought too.

94
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:38,240
Simply put, things like jewelry

95
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,240
and bags.

96
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,800
But apart from gifts,

97
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,680
a sense of ceremony is also important.

98
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,960
Especially for occasions like birthdays,

99
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:47,020
there must be a romantic atmosphere.

100
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:49,840
I've taught you all my tricks.

101
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,800
You have to comprehend it well.

102
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,080
An Yufan.

103
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,160
Don't blame me for not waiting for you.

104
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,160
It's really too dangerous here.

105
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,240
I can't stay here for long.

106
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,760
Yin Zixi,

107
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,290
what are you doing here?

108
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,760
Here she comes.

109
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,560
Boss, Yin Zixi is out.

110
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,800
Oh no, I can't control myself again.

111
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:33,960
Oh no.

112
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,760
Zixi.

113
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,240
I like you.

114
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,360
Be my girlfriend.

115
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:53,000
Together! Together!

116
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:58,000
Yin Zixi.

117
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,560
I won't give her to you.

118
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,320
She is my girlfriend.

119
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,880
Are you okay?

120
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,159
What you just said,

121
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,680
is it true?

122
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,600
Yin Zixi.

123
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,720
I like you.

124
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,840
Assistant Casting Director Xi Chongjing

125
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,720
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

126
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,680
Production Vehicle Yi Mingle

127
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,560
Yitong
